data.description: Pretty home with an enormous landscaped back yard boasting huge tree, bushes, and plenty of privacy.  This 3 bedroom, 2 bath charmer in Corrales Heights is a great home in a fantastic neighborhood.   Shopping, parks and schools are all nearby.   Move in ready, but a little paint and a few small updates will polish this gem.   Enjoy tiled floors in main living areas and freshly cleaned carpets in the bedrooms.  The Washer and Dryer are included with the sale.  Seller lives out of state, so will not do small repairs.  Don't miss this one!!
